name: San Pietro
description:
During our trip to Venice in June of 2017, my wife and I were instantly enchanted by the infinite beauty of the Italian 'Floating City'. We wanted to explore every alley (calle) and canal that was off the beaten path and hopefully catch a glimpse of how local Venetians went about their days.

THE VENETIAN SERIES is a photo-journal series of some of my favorite scenes from that unforgettable trip. The goal was to capture just a little piece of the indescribable feeling of being there and share it with friends and family.

All photos shot and edited directly on iPhone. All proceeds from the primary and secondary sales (15% royalty) of this account will go towards supporting other photography artists on tezos platforms.
